result:
.order_detail

        border-bottom 1px solid #E8EAED
        .box-title
            padding-top 20px
            font-size 16px
            color #333
        .msg-wrapper
            margin-top 15px
            padding-bottom 10px
            .msg-item
                display flex
                .item
                    flex 1

        align-items center
        img

            height 36px
            border-radius 4px
            margin-right 10px
